  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b92\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 - \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bae\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b8a\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Handover of money from the President's House to the court - Order to submit a report explaining the reason for the delay",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Crores of money recovered by protesters from Room 4 of the Presidential Palace was handed over to the Colombo - Fort Neetiwan Court today (29). The money was handed over to the court by the Colombo Madhi Zone Crime Prevention Bureau.",
        "Focusing on the video of the protestors handing over one crore 78 lakh 50 thousand rupees to the officer in charge of the Fort police station, the four persons who were on camera were arrested by the officers of the Colombo Central Zone Crime Investigation Bureau under the order of the Colombo Deputy Inspector General of Police.",
        "When they were produced in court yesterday (28), following the arguments of Senior Presidential Counsel Rienzi Arsakularatna, who appeared for them, the Fort Justice issued an order to hand over this amount to the court.",
        "Meanwhile, the judge has ordered the director of the Zonal Crime Investigation Bureau to explain to the court, including why more than 3 weeks have passed since the protestors handed over the money, why there was a delay in handing it over to the court, and why not even a report was submitted to the court in this regard."
      ],
